{"msg_id": "t001", "timestamp": "2026-04-10T09:00:00+08:00", "sender": {"wechat_id": "student_alice", "nickname": "Alice"}, "type": "text", "content": "请问 C5 的仓库名字需要特定格式吗？", "media_ref": null, "reply_to": null}
{"msg_id": "t002", "timestamp": "2026-04-10T09:03:00+08:00", "sender": {"wechat_id": "teacher_richard", "nickname": "Richard老师"}, "type": "text", "content": "是的，仓库名必须是 username.github.io 这种格式才能启用 GitHub Pages", "media_ref": null, "reply_to": "t001"}
{"msg_id": "t003", "timestamp": "2026-04-10T09:05:00+08:00", "sender": {"wechat_id": "student_bob", "nickname": "Bob"}, "type": "text", "content": "C5 提交需要包含哪些文件？", "media_ref": null, "reply_to": null}
{"msg_id": "t004", "timestamp": "2026-04-10T09:07:00+08:00", "sender": {"wechat_id": "teacher_richard", "nickname": "Richard老师"}, "type": "text", "content": "需要包含 index.html、README.md 和 AI日志三个文件", "media_ref": null, "reply_to": "t003"}
{"msg_id": "t005", "timestamp": "2026-04-10T09:10:00+08:00", "sender": {"wechat_id": "student_carol", "nickname": "Carol"}, "type": "text", "content": "我 push 的时候报错了 Permission denied (publickey)，怎么解决？", "media_ref": null, "reply_to": null}
{"msg_id": "t006", "timestamp": "2026-04-10T09:12:00+08:00", "sender": {"wechat_id": "ta_ethan", "nickname": "Ethan助教"}, "type": "text", "content": "需要先配置 SSH key，步骤是：1. ssh-keygen 生成密钥 2. 把公钥添加到 GitHub Settings > SSH keys", "media_ref": null, "reply_to": "t005"}
{"msg_id": "t007", "timestamp": "2026-04-10T09:15:00+08:00", "sender": {"wechat_id": "student_dave", "nickname": "Dave"}, "type": "text", "content": "C8 Bronze Level 的 wechat_bridge.py 这是我完成的", "media_ref": null, "reply_to": null}
{"msg_id": "t008", "timestamp": "2026-04-10T09:16:00+08:00", "sender": {"wechat_id": "student_dave", "nickname": "Dave"}, "type": "file", "content": "[文件] 张浩_C8_L1_AI日志.md", "media_ref": "path/to/file.md", "reply_to": null}
{"msg_id": "t009", "timestamp": "2026-04-10T09:20:00+08:00", "sender": {"wechat_id": "student_alice", "nickname": "Alice"}, "type": "text", "content": "git commit 之后 push 到 GitHub 为什么网页没有更新？", "media_ref": null, "reply_to": null}
{"msg_id": "t010", "timestamp": "2026-04-10T09:22:00+08:00", "sender": {"wechat_id": "ta_ethan", "nickname": "Ethan助教"}, "type": "text", "content": "GitHub Pages 有几分钟的延迟，等1-2分钟刷新就好了。也可以去 Settings > Pages 看 deployment 状态", "media_ref": null, "reply_to": "t009"}
{"msg_id": "t011", "timestamp": "2026-04-10T10:00:00+08:00", "sender": {"wechat_id": "teacher_richard", "nickname": "Richard老师"}, "type": "text", "content": "@所有人 C5 的 deadline 是本周日晚上23:59，请大家在截止时间前提交", "media_ref": null, "reply_to": null}
