{"msg_id": "t013", "timestamp": "2026-04-10T10:30:00+08:00", "sender": {"wechat_id": "student_carol", "nickname": "Carol"}, "type": "text", "content": "wechat-cli init 的时候报错 task_for_pid failed: 5 是什么意思？", "media_ref": null, "reply_to": null}
{"msg_id": "t014", "timestamp": "2026-04-10T10:32:00+08:00", "sender": {"wechat_id": "student_dave", "nickname": "Dave"}, "type": "text", "content": "这个是 macOS 安全限制，需要用 sudo 运行，而且微信需要重新签名。运行 sudo codesign --force --deep --sign - /Applications/WeChat.app 就能解决", "media_ref": null, "reply_to": "t013"}
