{"msg_id": "t017", "timestamp": "2026-04-10T11:15:00+08:00", "sender": {"wechat_id": "student_eve", "nickname": "Eve"}, "type": "text", "content": "Python 里面怎么读取 jsonl 文件？", "media_ref": null, "reply_to": null}
{"msg_id": "t018", "timestamp": "2026-04-10T11:17:00+08:00", "sender": {"wechat_id": "ta_ethan", "nickname": "Ethan助教"}, "type": "text", "content": "用 with open('file.jsonl') as f: 然后 for line in f: json.loads(line) 逐行解析就行", "media_ref": null, "reply_to": "t017"}
{"msg_id": "t019", "timestamp": "2026-04-10T14:00:00+08:00", "sender": {"wechat_id": "student_frank", "nickname": "Frank"}, "type": "text", "content": "C8 的 Property Graph 用什么数据库比较好？", "media_ref": null, "reply_to": null}
{"msg_id": "t020", "timestamp": "2026-04-10T14:02:00+08:00", "sender": {"wechat_id": "teacher_richard", "nickname": "Richard老师"}, "type": "text", "content": "Bronze/Silver 级别用 SQLite + JSON 就够了，轻量方便。如果要做 Platinum 可以考虑 Neo4j 或 NetworkX", "media_ref": null, "reply_to": "t019"}
